# AsianCharacter

This gem provides image for Chinese characters 

## Installation

Add this line to your application's Gemfile:

    gem 'asian_character'

And then execute:

    $ bundle

Or install it yourself as:

    $ gem install asian_character_image

## Usage

    require 'asian_character_image'

    word = AsianCharacter::Word.new('0000e006','24') # the first param is the unicode of this character, and the second param is the size of this chracter

    #to get character image url
    url = word.image_url #return http://chinese.biodinfo.org/chinesefiles/PicDB/0000e0/24/0000e006.jpg

